# AI Agent Skills

This directory contains **Agent Skills** for this project. Skills provide domain-specific patterns, conventions, and guardrails that help AI coding assistants understand project-specific requirements.

## How to Use Skills

Skills are automatically discovered by the AI agent. To manually load a skill during a session:

```
Read skills/{skill-name}/SKILL.md
```

